WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: tfHBfp6scUA

NOTE Language: en

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:52.240
Today it's such a pleasure to be here again,

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:54.920
in Brighton;

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:58.880
and, slowly and steadily, I find

00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:04.040
Sahaja Yoga is settling down in this place.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:09.640
When I first came to Brighton just to visit,

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:15.880
I felt there must be many seekers in this place,

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:19.600
who might have been lost

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:25.640
and always had a great hope

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:31.840
that one day they will be able to come to reality.

00:01:34.080 --> 00:01:39.120
Today specially is a very great day

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:45.320
because today is the birthday of Lord Buddha.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:48.600
And in the morning, I talked to Sahaja Yogis

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:51.560
about His great incarnation,

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:54.520
and how He came on this earth

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:58.200
and He got His realization,

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:00.600
and then how He tried to spread

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:04.800
the message of realizations to others.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:07.680
Many people believe and think

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:12.480
that Christ was an atheist … Buddha was an atheist,

00:02:12.680 --> 00:02:18.680
while Christ was a person, believer in God.

00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:25.600
And some people prefer Buddha to Jesus Christ.

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:29.720
It's something very amazing is that …

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:35.000
that when the people are born

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:38.440
in the particular circumstances,

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:41.320
they have to talk about things

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:46.720
which are very, very important at that point of time.

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:52.600
At the time when Buddha came on this earth in India,

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:57.160
we had too many ritualism of Brahmanism

00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:03.360
and conditioning of the teachings

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:07.800
of those money-makers and commercializers

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:13.160
who wanted to make money in the name of God

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:16.800
and in the name of religion.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:19.320
So, to neutralize all that,

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:25.040
He decided not to talk at all, at all about

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:30.080
God,

00:03:30.440 --> 00:03:35.840
about any particular religious ways,

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:40.160
but He said that you keep to the middle path of life,

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:43.160
eightfold middle path of life,

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:47.280
and that you first get your Self-realization.

00:03:47.480 --> 00:03:53.480
To Him it was very important that one should get Self-realization.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.000
And that's what

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:02.200
He wanted to give as a message

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:06.480
and divert the attention of the people

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:10.960
from the idea of God or incarnation —

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:13.440
for the time being —

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:18.720
because He wanted to show that Self-realization is very important

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:22.280
and that without Self-realization you cannot understand God

00:04:22.480 --> 00:04:25.480
or Divine Power.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:31.920
So He was not an atheist.

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:40.080
He and Christ, I would say, were in a way contemporary,

00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:46.280
but Christ came later,

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:52.280
and Buddha came about five hundred years before Christ.

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:55.200
They are so much related to each other,

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:57.840
so much close to each other,

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.400
so much identified with each other,

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:03.800
as if they are part and parcel of one being.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:08.600
That only you can understand when you get your Self-realization.

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:13.000
Christ has said: “Those who are not against Me are with Me.”

00:05:13.200 --> 00:05:17.400
Who are “those”, who are not against Him?

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:24.040
Because we have no knowledge as to real the origin of Christ,

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:26.640
from where He came, what was His origin,

00:05:26.840 --> 00:05:28.880
how He was created in the heaven,

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:32.680
how He is the Son of God.

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:37.640
Whatever we see today as a person who came on this earth

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:43.200
to teach us about His father, God Almighty,

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:47.680
we just believe into that part,

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:50.880
which is a very limited part of Christ,

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:54.800
and Bible cannot contain that great personality.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.760
In the same way, Buddha has been dumped

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:02.920
into very small dimensions.

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:07.840
Only two persons realized it; they got out of it.

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:10.400
One of them was Viditama,

00:06:10.600 --> 00:06:14.920
who went away to Japan and started the Zen system of religion.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:17.240
But even today if you see the Zen,

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:20.120
which was nothing but dhyana, the meditation,

00:06:20.320 --> 00:06:24.360
sahaja, spontaneous awakening —

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:30.760
is reduced to the same level as any other preaching.

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:34.440
I met the head of the Zen system.

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:36.640
He was very sick, and they brought him to Me

00:06:36.840 --> 00:06:38.600
because he wanted to be cured.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:43.320
And I was amazed that, not that he was a realized soul,

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:48.880
not at all a realized soul — but his Kundalini, which is the force

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:51.960
which is going to give him realization was all frozen.

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:55.880
And he had no desire to become self-realized.

00:06:56.080 --> 00:06:58.360
I talked to him, I was amazed.

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:00.400
And I said, “How is it,

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:03.680
that according to Zen you have to be a kashyapa?”

00:07:03.880 --> 00:07:08.560
Kashyapa means a person who is a realized soul.

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:12.760
That's the name of the university, as I told you yesterday in Lewes,

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:14.720
is the name of the university is kashyapa:

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:17.360
those who have no university,

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:20.680
in the sense, those who have the university of God.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:22.360
So he said, “Oh, that's over now,

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:25.160
God is not making anybody kashyapas now.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:27.800
Only from the sixth to the eighth century,

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:31.040
in two hundred years, there were only twenty-six kashyapas,

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:34.960
after that there were none. And I don't hope to be one.”

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.440
I said, “Why not?”

00:07:36.640 --> 00:07:38.640
He said, “No, I have no hopes about it,

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:42.680
I'm just now appointed as the head of Zen, so I'm there,

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:45.840
but we don't get kashyapas these days at all.”

00:07:46.040 --> 00:07:48.440
So with that he doomed all the hopes

00:07:48.640 --> 00:07:51.280
of all the people to become Zen,

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:54.440
to become person who knows,

00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:58.040
person who is a realized soul.

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:03.440
This one was very shocking to Me

00:08:03.640 --> 00:08:08.000
because Zen is something so great.

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:11.560
There's so much expressive of Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:11.760 --> 00:08:15.720
You cannot understand Zen unless and until you are a realized soul.

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:19.240
Even Bible you can't understand, you can't understand Gita,

00:08:19.440 --> 00:08:21.080
you can't understand anything

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:24.080
unless and until you are a realized soul.

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:28.280
The second person who really emerged out of it,

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:30.000
all this ritualism and all that

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:33.480
that they had created out of Buddha's life,

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:37.400
was Lao Tze,

00:08:37.640 --> 00:08:39.600
who preached about Tao.

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:43.640
Tao is the all-pervading Divine Power.

00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:46.520
Power of love.

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:50.800
When He talked about it, He explained about it,

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:56.400
and He started another group of people,

00:08:56.600 --> 00:08:59.240
who were to be given realization.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:02.720
But that also today, I find, has become “Tao-ism”.

00:09:02.920 --> 00:09:06.400
Everything becomes “ism” — means “imprisoned”.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:10.160
It's not living, it's not there,

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.640
it's just a thought of Tao people read.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:16.680
I have seen people … there's one gentleman in India

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:19.400
who has written a complete book on Tao.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.840
He's not even a realized soul.

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:24.800
What is he writing? I was just wondering, with his blind eyes,

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:29.600
what is he describing, what colors can he describe?

00:09:29.880 --> 00:09:33.600
So you must know that you have to be self-realized first.

00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:36.280
Then see for yourself.

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:42.440
Then you will know whether there is spirit or not,

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:45.680
then you will know whether there are roots

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:50.800
to this tree that has grown outside,

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:55.840
then you will know where there is God or not.

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:58.960
Then you will know what these incarnations

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:01.280
have any meaning or not.

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:04.800
Just before that just to sit down and criticize

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:07.440
is not a sensible thing.

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:12.600
That's why Buddha … who occupies a very special place

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:16.440
within our being itself, He resides on this side.

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.960
This is the place where our ego is attached,

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:24.960
and He is the one who really controls our ego.

00:10:25.640 --> 00:10:28.360
So this Buddha

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:32.720
also is such a part and parcel,

00:10:32.920 --> 00:10:37.240
is to be understood only after you have got realization.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:41.240
Without that you are still incomplete.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:45.920
You are not that by which you will know.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:50.720
Like Krishna has said: “Atmanyevatmana tushtah” [BhG 2-55].

00:10:50.920 --> 00:10:55.080
Through the atma, through the spirit only you are going to know God.

00:10:55.280 --> 00:10:57.520
Not through with this mental projection,

00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:00.840
with these eyes, with these senses but through the spirit.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:04.160
And where is the spirit within us?

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:07.360
The spirit lies in our heart

00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:12.160
and is the reflection of God Almighty.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.800
It's called as a kshetragya,

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:20.080
means “the one who knows the field of our action”.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:23.960
The one who sees what we are doing,

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:28.440
who is the witness of what we are doing.

00:11:28.640 --> 00:11:32.840
But He is not in our attention.

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:37.520
That gentleman wants to come, please come.

00:11:38.760 --> 00:11:42.680
He is not in our attention.

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:45.760
And if He is not in our attention,

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:49.480
we do not know how to connect

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:54.160
ourselves with Him to have a rapport with Him,

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:56.000
to understand Him.

00:11:56.200 --> 00:12:01.600
That's why first this spirit has to be brought in our own attention.

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:03.960
That's the most important thing,

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:08.240
and because this is not with us,

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:12.640
we are still incomplete, we make mistakes.

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:17.280
Because the absolute thing that is within us is the spirit,

00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:20.040
while we live on a relative world.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:22.360
Today somebody comes and says to  you all right.

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:24.680
Just now, when we were coming, there was a gentleman

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:28.520
who handed over a card to Me,

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:31.000
about … something about Christ.

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:34.640
He's telling Me about Christ, I really must laugh at it.

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:39.200
But supposing tomorrow Christ comes and stands before you;

00:12:39.400 --> 00:12:44.440
will you be able to recognize Him, or will you crucify Him again?

00:12:44.840 --> 00:12:48.040
How will you recognize Him? How will you recognize Buddha?

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:54.240
Have you got sensitivity to know who is Christ?

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:58.320
It's very easy to, you see, to represent Christ,

00:12:58.520 --> 00:13:00.280
it's very easy because they think

00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:04.360
that, after all, you see, everybody has a right to do what they like.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:09.480
Even Hitler talked of God, can you imagine?

00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:11.800
Hitler talked of God!

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:17.360
Everyone thinks he has got right to talk of God, to describe Him!

00:13:17.560 --> 00:13:20.680
But first of all you must know

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:25.120
that no use deceiving ourselves,

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:29.520
we have to get our Self-realization.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:33.600
We have to know ourselves first of all.

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:38.040
Now, Buddha's attitude towards His attainment was

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:41.560
that He was actually

00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:48.320
touched by the miseries of the world.

00:13:48.520 --> 00:13:54.520
He saw a person who was sick. He saw a man who was dead.

00:13:54.760 --> 00:13:58.640
He saw an old man. All these things worked on His mind,

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:03.120
and He started thinking: “Why these miseries are there?”

00:14:03.320 --> 00:14:07.880
So the whole search came

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:14.080
through the understanding for others.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:18.640
That takes too much time because you have to go on neutralizing:

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:23.920
“Not this, not this, not wife, not children, not family…”

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:26.680
You go on negating, negating, negating;

00:14:26.880 --> 00:14:32.240
all your lives you go on, one after another. Doesn't work out.

00:14:32.440 --> 00:14:35.200
The other way is simpler — could be …

00:14:35.400 --> 00:14:38.000
which of course by Buddha's attainment only

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:40.000
has been made even better …

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:44.000
all of them have done something for us within ourselves —

00:14:44.200 --> 00:14:48.680
that first we look after ourselves,

00:14:48.880 --> 00:14:51.480
find out about ourselves.

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:55.640
Are we realized souls?

00:14:55.840 --> 00:14:58.840
Are we Buddhas?

00:14:59.160 --> 00:15:02.960
Are we the people who know?

00:15:04.440 --> 00:15:06.880
Let us be honest.

00:15:07.080 --> 00:15:09.720
Then we have to know.

00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:13.920
Now, what is the way to know is the point.

00:15:16.040 --> 00:15:22.040
Now, if I say that you will know — in your evolutionary process.

00:15:23.640 --> 00:15:27.280
As you have evolved to be a human being, you will be evolved

00:15:27.480 --> 00:15:30.000
to be a realized soul.

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:34.840
But there's a little difference as to what has happened so far

00:15:35.040 --> 00:15:38.800
and what is going to happen later on.

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:44.520
So far, we have been evolved

00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:50.400
through a method which was beyond

00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:54.080
our freedom.

00:15:54.920 --> 00:15:59.680
The nature worked it out, the nature within us,

00:16:00.400 --> 00:16:04.160
the central force of evolution within us

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:07.880
has brought us to this position that from amoeba

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:11.320
today we are human beings.

00:16:11.560 --> 00:16:14.640
But at this stage, when we are human beings,

00:16:14.840 --> 00:16:20.840
to go further, there's a special mechanism.

00:16:23.040 --> 00:16:25.840
Like, till to make this instrument,

00:16:26.040 --> 00:16:30.520
we had to use other instruments to make it.

00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:34.120
Now, once the instrument is just ready,

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:40.320
we have to just plug this one to the mains, and it's done.

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:44.120
As if you are made

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:47.960
to be ready

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:53.200
to be plugged to the all-pervading Power;

00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:59.400
and by some special, spontaneous method

00:17:00.120 --> 00:17:03.200
done by the living force within us,

00:17:03.400 --> 00:17:07.240
we have to be plugged to the mains.

00:17:11.040 --> 00:17:13.040
But the difference

00:17:13.240 --> 00:17:19.240
between a human being and other animals

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:25.040
is this that human beings were given their freedom.

00:17:26.080 --> 00:17:30.960
At the stage of, say, Adam and Eve,

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:36.640
if people would not have gone too far with their freedom,

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:38.920
it would have been much easier

00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:42.920
to give realization to people at that time.

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:46.600
But when freedom is given,

00:17:47.120 --> 00:17:52.120
then people misuse it. Or, they want to use it.

00:17:52.320 --> 00:17:55.840
They don't want to obey, because to obey means, they think,

00:17:56.040 --> 00:17:58.160
there is no freedom.

00:17:58.360 --> 00:18:02.160
And that's how, when they started using their freedom,

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:06.640
they had to do things which were wrong,

00:18:06.840 --> 00:18:12.280
which were anti-life, which were anti-evolution,

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:17.360
without realizing what they were doing.

00:18:19.200 --> 00:18:22.360
When it reached the stage

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:27.200
when people found that was wrong, they gave it up.

00:18:27.600 --> 00:18:30.520
Then another thing they tried,

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:34.280
it was like an error being corrected.

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:36.240
Then they corrected it.

00:18:36.440 --> 00:18:38.600
That's how human beings have been trying,

00:18:38.800 --> 00:18:43.040
experimenting with this, experimenting with that;

00:18:44.280 --> 00:18:47.280
and then they come to a point where they say, “Given up now,

00:18:47.480 --> 00:18:50.160
it's too much.”

00:18:50.360 --> 00:18:54.560
That's the best point, I think, as Buddha had reached;

00:18:54.760 --> 00:19:00.760
He was so tired, lying down under a banyan tree —

00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:04.960
and He got His realization.

00:19:06.200 --> 00:19:09.880
So now I am here before you to tell you

00:19:10.080 --> 00:19:12.720
what is the mechanism.

00:19:12.920 --> 00:19:18.120
You should not in any case accept Me fully, you should not.

00:19:18.320 --> 00:19:22.800
That would be wrong on My part and wrong on your part

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:28.000
because you're free, you are free, not to accept or to accept.

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:30.080
But you have to keep yourself open

00:19:30.280 --> 00:19:34.080
because this is a new category of knowledge

00:19:34.280 --> 00:19:37.640
which I am telling you about.

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:41.160
About the roots, about which you do not know.

00:19:41.360 --> 00:19:43.400
You know only about the tree,

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:46.560
but I want to tell you about the roots.

00:19:46.760 --> 00:19:51.480
The best thing would be, first and foremost,

00:19:52.280 --> 00:19:56.520
to be able to enter into the roots.

00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:59.720
But you cannot!

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:03.000
As the human mind is,

00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:07.560
it wants to know everything about everything first of all.

00:20:07.920 --> 00:20:10.480
But see, here,

00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:14.560
if you have to enter into this room

00:20:16.440 --> 00:20:19.720
and there is no light, somebody tells you,

00:20:19.920 --> 00:20:23.000
“All right, press that button and you get all the lights.”

