Whatever I may talk for hours together,

00:22:10.920 --> 00:22:13.360
you will not get your realization.

00:22:13.560 --> 00:22:16.960
It's a happening that has to take place within you.

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:19.280
Unless and until this happening takes place,

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:21.920
you cannot get your realization.

00:22:22.120 --> 00:22:27.680
And it's a happening which is to be experienced by you, not by Me.

00:22:27.880 --> 00:22:30.280
It is to be felt by you,

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:35.680
and by this happening you have to feel your own powers,

00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:40.120
your own glory, and your own purpose.

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:45.480
So far, we do not know the purpose of human life,

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:49.280
why human beings were created from amoeba stage.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:54.280
But then you know what is the purpose of this life.

00:22:55.360 --> 00:22:58.200
I'm sure they must have told you something about Kundalini.

00:22:58.400 --> 00:23:01.400
Jason, did you tell them?

00:23:01.840 --> 00:23:04.840
Not much?

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:07.840
YOGI: Very little, Mother.
SHRI MATAJI: Eh?

00:23:08.040 --> 00:23:09.800
YOGI: Very little, Mother.

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:12.920
SHRI MATAJI: What's he saying?
YOGI: That he [UNCLEAR] very little.

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:15.040
SHRI MATAJI: All right.

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:20.160
So now here I would like to tell you something about it,

00:23:20.400 --> 00:23:23.640
which you should take as a hypothesis just now

00:23:23.840 --> 00:23:28.080
and try to understand. It's not very difficult, to begin with.

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:30.760
And later on, as soon as you get your realization,

00:23:30.960 --> 00:23:33.960
it's the easiest thing to do.

00:23:34.480 --> 00:23:38.360
We have within ourselves seven centers,

00:23:38.560 --> 00:23:43.600
placed in our medulla oblongata and in the brain.

00:23:43.800 --> 00:23:48.080
The first one lies below the triangular bone,

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:50.320
which is called as sacrum,

00:23:50.520 --> 00:23:53.200
and it's called as the Mooladhara center,

00:23:53.400 --> 00:23:58.840
which means “the support of the roots”.

00:23:59.040 --> 00:24:01.960
It is the support of the roots.

00:24:02.160 --> 00:24:08.160
And this center embodies our innocence.

00:24:08.840 --> 00:24:14.080
The second one … and of course it manifests outside in the gross,

00:24:14.280 --> 00:24:17.120
the pelvic plexus.

00:24:17.320 --> 00:24:22.240
Now, the second one is the one that emerges from the third one,

00:24:22.440 --> 00:24:27.800
which is called as the Nabhi Chakra, the third one;

00:24:28.160 --> 00:24:32.400
and the one that emerges from that

00:24:32.600 --> 00:24:36.680
is the second one, called as the Swadishthana.

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:39.480
Now, the Swadishthana Chakra in the gross —

00:24:39.680 --> 00:24:42.360
because these are subtle centers, in the medulla oblongata —

00:24:42.560 --> 00:24:48.320
but outside, in the gross, it manifests

00:24:48.520 --> 00:24:51.040
what we call the aortic plexus.

00:24:51.240 --> 00:24:55.360
If there are doctors here, they'll understand what I'm talking about.

00:24:55.560 --> 00:24:57.800
Now, if you go further,

00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:04.000
the Nabhi Chakra manifests outside what we call as the solar plexus.

00:25:04.360 --> 00:25:09.720
Above that is the center that we call as the Heart center,

00:25:09.920 --> 00:25:13.160
Anahata Chakra, cardiac center,

00:25:13.360 --> 00:25:16.280
which manifests outside

00:25:16.480 --> 00:25:19.520
the cardiac plexus.

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:23.560
And it has got, again, the left and right side.

00:25:23.840 --> 00:25:29.480
Then we have the center at the root of our neck,

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:32.120
which is called as the Vishuddhi Chakra

00:25:32.320 --> 00:25:35.640
and which manifests outside

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:39.800
the cervical plexus.

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:43.520
Above that, here where you see the red mark on My head —

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:46.520
this is just the window of that center —

00:25:46.720 --> 00:25:49.360
between the pituitary and the pineal body,

00:25:49.560 --> 00:25:53.320
where the optic chiasma cross each other in the center,

00:25:53.520 --> 00:25:58.000
is a very important center called as Agnya Chakra,

00:25:58.200 --> 00:26:02.280
which looks after our ego and our superego,

00:26:02.480 --> 00:26:05.160
which you can see there passing through that,

00:26:05.360 --> 00:26:07.520
crossing over like that.

00:26:07.720 --> 00:26:11.240
And on the top of that is the last seventh center,

00:26:11.440 --> 00:26:14.320
called as the Sahasrara,

00:26:14.520 --> 00:26:17.800
meaning “one thousand petals center”.

00:26:18.000 --> 00:26:20.000
And that's the center …

00:26:20.200 --> 00:26:23.800
is just in the limbic area,

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:29.600
and when you pierce through that in the fontanelle area,

00:26:30.000 --> 00:26:35.000
you feel the cool breeze of the Kundalini, or the Holy Ghost,

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:38.200
coming out of your head.

00:26:38.440 --> 00:26:41.800
This has to happen.

00:26:43.320 --> 00:26:45.560
You cannot give false certificates.

00:26:45.760 --> 00:26:49.880
You have to feel the cool breeze coming out of your head.

00:26:50.080 --> 00:26:53.720
You have to feel the cool breeze in your hands;

00:26:53.920 --> 00:26:59.600
that means you have to feel the all-pervading Power of God,

00:27:00.040 --> 00:27:01.400
of Love,

00:27:01.600 --> 00:27:05.160
which is called as Brahma Shakti in Sanskrit language

00:27:05.360 --> 00:27:11.000
and in the Bible is called as the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:14.680
For the first time you have to feel it

00:27:14.880 --> 00:27:19.720
in your hands, in your central nervous system.

00:27:19.920 --> 00:27:24.880
Because the seat of your spirit is here,

00:27:25.080 --> 00:27:28.880
but the spirit resides in the heart.

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:32.440
Once the seat is touched by the awakened Kundalini —

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:35.840
which is in the triangular bone, if you see —

00:27:36.040 --> 00:27:38.640
then you start feeling

00:27:38.840 --> 00:27:42.720
the first the cool breeze and then in the hand,

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:46.600
you start feeling the cool breeze flowing from you.

00:27:46.800 --> 00:27:52.280
Thus you manifest the power of your spirit.

00:27:53.000 --> 00:27:57.960
It's a happening that has to take place. It's a living happening.

00:27:58.160 --> 00:28:01.320
It's very easy to tell people, “All right, now you start jumping.”

00:28:01.520 --> 00:28:04.120
You see, anybody can jump, what's so great in jumping?

00:28:04.320 --> 00:28:06.400
Or if somebody says, “All right, take out your clothes.”

00:28:06.600 --> 00:28:09.880
What's so great? Or, “Color your clothes in this way.”

00:28:10.080 --> 00:28:12.800
Nothing so special, anybody can do it.

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:17.440
But can you take out cool breeze out of your head?

00:28:19.680 --> 00:28:22.160
Your own head.

00:28:22.360 --> 00:28:26.320
And when you get it, you can do it to others.

00:28:26.520 --> 00:28:30.640
Even from the others' heads you can take it out.

00:28:31.080 --> 00:28:35.600
This is the way it has to happen, the time has come.

00:28:35.800 --> 00:28:40.560
This is a very special time, when so many seekers are born,

00:28:40.760 --> 00:28:45.360
so many of them, in millions and millions of them;

00:28:45.560 --> 00:28:48.920
and so many are lost also,

00:28:49.120 --> 00:28:53.200
because of various reasons, because of attack on them.

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:58.120
From very childhood, a person who is a seeker is attacked.

00:28:58.400 --> 00:29:01.680
Ultimately, his ego can attack.

00:29:01.880 --> 00:29:04.440
He may have his own mental projections built in,

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:07.880
he may have horrible gurus, taking out money from him.

00:29:08.080 --> 00:29:10.720
And there'll be people … will be maneuvering them,

00:29:10.920 --> 00:29:13.960
there'll be people who'll be creating projection things

00:29:14.160 --> 00:29:17.120
just to engulf them.

00:29:17.320 --> 00:29:21.160
But to an Indian, it is easy — if they are Indians, of course;

00:29:21.360 --> 00:29:24.960
if they are uprooted people and all are westernized, then I can't say.

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:27.280
But to a normal Indian, they know

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:30.840
it is the Kundalini awakening that gives you realization.

00:29:31.040 --> 00:29:34.480
I don't have to tell them that this is so.

00:29:34.680 --> 00:29:37.280
They know. They are not naive.

00:29:37.480 --> 00:29:39.360
But in the Bible also it is written

00:29:39.560 --> 00:29:43.600
that “I will appear before you like tongues of flames,”

00:29:43.800 --> 00:29:46.440
and actually, when you see the Sahasrara,

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:51.480
it looks likes beautiful flames in seven colors,

00:29:51.680 --> 00:29:54.360
most harmless, silently;

00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:57.800
like this flame

00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:01.120
but very longish flames,

00:30:01.320 --> 00:30:05.200
and silently burning and opening out,

00:30:05.400 --> 00:30:07.640
very cooling flames.

00:30:07.840 --> 00:30:11.240
Even this flame can give you cool breeze.

00:30:11.440 --> 00:30:13.080
It has happened with many;

00:30:13.280 --> 00:30:15.800
and how it works out, that we have to see.

00:30:16.000 --> 00:30:19.760
It's fantastic! It's too much to believe.

00:30:19.960 --> 00:30:22.480
First of all, we have no faith in ourselves,

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:25.560
we don't know how can we get realization so easily.

00:30:25.760 --> 00:30:28.960
People had to do this, people had to do that.

00:30:29.160 --> 00:30:31.200
But time has come.

00:30:31.400 --> 00:30:34.320
You have done everything in your previous lives.

00:30:34.520 --> 00:30:37.520
You have starved yourself,

00:30:38.080 --> 00:30:40.240
you have roamed about,

00:30:40.440 --> 00:30:42.960
you have done all the tapasyas, the penance,

00:30:43.160 --> 00:30:47.360
and today is the time for you to get realization.

00:30:47.560 --> 00:30:49.400
And that's what it is.

00:30:49.600 --> 00:30:53.000
But why doubt it? You don't have to pay for it.

00:30:53.200 --> 00:30:57.200
Nothing is selling here, you know that. Nothing is selling.

00:30:57.400 --> 00:31:02.480
Actually, you cannot sell God. You cannot sell God!

00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:06.640
Those who sell are committing sins.

00:31:07.600 --> 00:31:10.480
How can you sell love?

00:31:10.680 --> 00:31:13.480
Love is not a saleable quality.

00:31:13.680 --> 00:31:16.880
Then the love of God, how can you sell?

00:31:17.080 --> 00:31:20.160
But we are so attracted by commercializing and all that.

00:31:20.360 --> 00:31:22.760
Because everything is so commercialized.

00:31:22.960 --> 00:31:25.480
And so traditional now that, for people

00:31:25.680 --> 00:31:28.240
who says that you cannot pay for your realization,

00:31:28.440 --> 00:31:31.920
they just can't understand how can it be.

00:31:32.200 --> 00:31:35.160
Get out of this, get out of it!

00:31:35.360 --> 00:31:40.360
And just know that commercializing is a sin

00:31:40.560 --> 00:31:46.000
if you try to do that in the realm of Divine.

00:31:46.200 --> 00:31:50.120
It's a sinful thing. Anybody who has done that is wrong.

00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:53.160
Christ had taken a big hunter and hit all those people

00:31:53.360 --> 00:31:59.120
who were selling near that church. That's what it is.

00:31:59.320 --> 00:32:02.160
Today we find in all the churches, all the temples,

00:32:02.360 --> 00:32:06.120
mosques and everywhere — are nothing but commercializing.

00:32:06.320 --> 00:32:08.960
But that doesn't mean that those people

00:32:09.160 --> 00:32:13.800
who propounded those great ideals

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:16.800
to balance yourself

00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:20.120
on your Void as we call it —

00:32:20.320 --> 00:32:26.320
they gave you the Ten Commandments to balance yourself —

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:28.800
that they were wrong,

00:32:29.000 --> 00:32:32.560
that they did it just as a mental projection.

00:32:32.760 --> 00:32:35.760
It's a fact, you have to balance yourself!

00:32:35.960 --> 00:32:38.320
All of them tried to balance you,

00:32:38.520 --> 00:32:41.840
gave you a method of moderation.

00:32:42.040 --> 00:32:46.040
For what is this moderation?

00:32:46.240 --> 00:32:48.160
Is for the ascent.

00:32:48.360 --> 00:32:52.120
If you do not have balance in life, you cannot move.

00:32:52.320 --> 00:32:56.720
Imagine a car going on two wheels on one side.

00:32:57.200 --> 00:33:00.640
Even if there's a bicycle, you have to balance it.

00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:04.760
You just can't ride a bicycle if you don't know how to balance it.

00:33:04.960 --> 00:33:08.360
So this balance was to be established, and that's why

00:33:08.560 --> 00:33:13.720
they propounded all these great ideals for all of you.

00:33:14.360 --> 00:33:17.880
And all this is for your ascent

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:21.520
and not to be just settled down with that balance.

00:33:21.720 --> 00:33:25.680
You have to ascend, and that ascent

00:33:25.880 --> 00:33:30.280
is now very simple and easy

00:33:30.480 --> 00:33:32.440
because the time has come.

00:33:32.640 --> 00:33:37.560
As I told you yesterday, on the tree of life

00:33:37.760 --> 00:33:42.800
there were very, very few flowers to begin with.

00:33:43.000 --> 00:33:48.160
But today, at the blossom time, there are so many seekers.

00:33:48.360 --> 00:33:52.240
A special category, the flowers as they call it.

00:33:52.440 --> 00:33:54.080
They are flowers, no doubt;

00:33:54.280 --> 00:33:58.560
when they called them flowers, it was true they were flowers —

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:02.560
but they went into wrong direction.

00:34:02.760 --> 00:34:07.720
They were definitely flowers to become fruits.

00:34:07.920 --> 00:34:10.320
And they will, God willing,

00:34:10.520 --> 00:34:13.920
all of them will have to become the fruits.

00:34:14.120 --> 00:34:17.120
May God bless you all!

